{"tid":1778464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大波幻幻韓妹比人打","createTime":"2019-12-11T03:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T09:02:26.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f61ec48aab3e7e7dfe1304dde00a979c47d7b663","tid":1778464,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"消息來源：（英文網站報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/qmlrrk7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fqmlrrk7&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=a2c70189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/qmlrrk7</a><br />\n<br />\n影片來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1204438456044314626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1204438456044314626&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=d9d2a861\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1204438456044314626&h=21af3b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1204438456044314626</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gJ8s7Ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgJ8s7Ef.jpg&h=898e3fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Busters 成員 Chaeyeon 在節目上被打的影片流出&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該節目在2019年12月10日錄影完後，一個粉絲上傳了一段影片，畫面顯示Chaeyeon有拉了一個男性藝人Choi Youngsoo的襯衫，看似要向他提問，才拉了襯衫不讓他走掉。<br />\n<br />\n然後看到Youngsoo被拉了襯衫之後，他猛烈地甩開Chaeyeon的手，並被指出用拳頭打了Chaeyeon的左手臂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q2mfRcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq2mfRcd.jpg&h=08709117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但打的瞬間，有另一位藝人經過粉絲的鏡頭前面，因此涉嫌打人的動作瞬間被擋住了，但是可以聽到影片中的毆打聲。<br />\n<br />\n打了一拳之後，Youngsoo憤怒地走開了，Chaeyeon驚呆了，但是Chaeyeon隨即給了笑容反應，Youngsoo往旁邊走掉時似乎嘴角也有上揚。<br />\n<br />\n粉絲對影片感到不安，不僅因為涉嫌毆打的問題，還因為Chaeyeon才15歲。<br />\n<br />\n但是，一些網友認為這可能是雙方的玩笑或遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，粉絲們都要求節目和Youngsoo做出解釋和聲明。"},{"pid":"aeae77e9aa13dfd7c52f3031283b97217dc7e9af","tid":1778464,"uid":167880,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"永遠最關建位都比人遮住"},{"pid":"872bba45f7a08091e925ee59a31a3bf6bebb3a21","tid":1778464,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"揸下波啫"},{"pid":"2ddaa5803adebcb6b225b40212c6c7ec4a1df286","tid":1778464,"uid":71632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aeae77e9aa13dfd7c52f3031283b97217dc7e9af","tid":1778464,"uid":167880,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"永遠最關建位都比人遮住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:48:07.000Z","msg":"咪係, 都睇唔到有幾大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9538078d31829ee41348fd08902a642d59719c","tid":1778464,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"872bba45f7a08091e925ee59a31a3bf6bebb3a21","tid":1778464,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"揸下波啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"弱智?"},{"pid":"f4ae6221dd5963da95b93d75809c68ababcceb1b","tid":1778464,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"Chaeyeon...<br />\n想起牙演了🚬"},{"pid":"0bedc9f730303be95cb222874a7aea5ef8d26846","tid":1778464,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ce869a1170bfa4f61b82ed72a57a6c2fa3a671","tid":1778464,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e2c497fabfb4453d24c4a751a8587990dac7c0","tid":1778464,"uid":89931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"872bba45f7a08091e925ee59a31a3bf6bebb3a21","tid":1778464,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-